{"tid":287411,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"關於縮時攝影 Time-lapse photography","createTime":"2017-06-17T11:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T17:25:01.000Z","uid":34240,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"469cfa056e3a3870678de6d7cd08abd6fce14375","tid":287411,"uid":34240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"BY WIKI:從接近一般正常的拍攝速率（介於每秒24張至每秒30張），到一天僅拍攝一張，甚至一週或者更長的間隔<br />\n<br />\n但係佢本黎拍出黎D畫面應該係斷斷續續GE, 點解到用正常24-30FPS咁PLAY番出黎個時會咁連續, 咁流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ada8e4497647389ea8ec16961eafab730f866","tid":287411,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"明唔明乜叫縮時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設24fps播出，姐係用24張相用1秒播哂出嚟，一日影一張的話，姐係一秒就播左24日嘅相，你放番慢嚟睇就知了。"},{"pid":"c3ff73846fdd6a5bf4df12d3e78cbf94adf85290","tid":287411,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:12:40.000Z","msg":"如果題材變化慢，一日一張都無問題"},{"pid":"f684e4801f9e36b7eea93a2c7e9a6218abd88f2d","tid":287411,"uid":21455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"睇過人影冰川好似影左唔知幾多個月定成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}